00:04:21.300 --> 00:04:26.339
Just like it sounds, we're asking, we're requesting of Jehovah and Jehovah encourages

00:04:26.339 --> 00:04:30.100
us to ask him for our needs.

00:04:30.100 --> 00:04:36.980
At Matthew 7, 7, Jesus said, keep on asking and it will be given you.

00:04:36.980 --> 00:04:42.939
Keep on seeking and you will find, keep on knocking and it will be open to you.

00:04:42.939 --> 00:04:48.259
And of course, Jesus gives us things we can pray for, our daily bread, forgiveness of

00:04:48.259 --> 00:04:52.899
our sins, deliverance from the evil one as a few examples.

00:04:52.899 --> 00:04:55.779
But now let's take supplication.

00:04:55.779 --> 00:05:02.100
The watchtower explains, the word means earnest and treaty, besieging prayer.

00:05:02.100 --> 00:05:09.540
