00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:12.800
kingdom hope, just to mention a few things.

00:06:12.800 --> 00:06:20.120
It is only right that we thank Jehovah for the things he has done is doing and will yet

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:22.319
do in the future.

00:06:22.319 --> 00:06:29.879
As Paul said at Ephesians 520, we should be always giving thanks to our God and Father

00:06:29.879 --> 00:06:32.199
